### `transactions_in`
Material Inward entries (from sellers to jobbers).

| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| [id](file:///c:/Users/moksh/Videos/Projects/Ongoing%20%20Projects/HP/client/src/components/Sidebar.jsx#12-76) | integer | Primary Key |
| `jobber_id` | integer | FK â†’ jobbers.id |
| `seller_id` | integer | FK â†’ sellers.id |
| `type1` | numeric | Material quantity (type 1) |
| `type2` | numeric | Material quantity (type 2) |
| `material` | varchar | Material description |
| [rate](file:///c:/Users/moksh/Videos/Projects/Ongoing%20%20Projects/HP/server/migrate.js#12-50) | numeric | Rate per unit |
| `amount` | numeric | Total amount |
| [date](file:///c:/Users/moksh/Videos/Projects/Ongoing%20%20Projects/HP/server/controllers/transactionController.js#46-51) | date | Transaction date |
| `w` | boolean | W flag |
| `b` | boolean | B flag |
| `a` | boolean | A flag |
| `remark` | text | Optional note |
| `created_at` | timestamp | Auto set on insert |

