## API Reference

**Base URL:** `http://localhost:5000`

---

### Masters

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/jobbers` | Fetch all jobbers |
| `POST` | `/api/jobbers` | Create a jobber â€” `{ name }` |
| `GET` | `/api/sellers` | Fetch all sellers |
| `POST` | `/api/sellers` | Create a seller â€” `{ name }` |
| `GET` | `/api/vendors` | Fetch all vendors |
| `POST` | `/api/vendors` | Create a vendor â€” `{ name }` |

---

### Transactions

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/transactions/in` | All material-in records |
| `POST` | `/api/transactions/in` | Create material-in record |
| `PUT` | `/api/transactions/in/:id` | Update material-in record |
| `DELETE` | `/api/transactions/in/:id` | Delete (requires `x-delete-password` header) |
| `GET` | `/api/transactions/out` | All material-out records |
| `POST` | `/api/transactions/out` | Create material-out record |
| `PUT` | `/api/transactions/out/:id` | Update material-out record |
| `DELETE` | `/api/transactions/out/:id` | Delete (requires `x-delete-password` header) |

---

### Reports

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/job-report/:jobberName` | Full jobber report (IN + OUT + OUT_ADJ) |
| `GET` | `/api/seller-report/:sellerName` | Full seller report (IN + IN_ADJ) |

---

### Jobber Adjustments

| Method | Endpoint | Body | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/adjustments/jobber/:jobberId` | â€” | Get all adjustments for a jobber |
| `POST` | `/api/adjustments` | `{ jobber_id, amount, date, remark }` | Create adjustment |
| `PUT` | `/api/adjustments/:id` | `{ amount, date, remark }` | Update adjustment |
| `DELETE` | `/api/adjustments/:id` | â€” | Delete (requires `x-delete-password` header) |

---

### Seller Adjustments

| Method | Endpoint | Body | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/seller-adjustments/seller/:sellerId` | â€” | Get all adjustments for a seller |
| `POST` | `/api/seller-adjustments` | `{ seller_id, amount, date, remark }` | Create adjustment |
| `PUT` | `/api/seller-adjustments/:id` | `{ amount, date, remark }` | Update adjustment |
| `DELETE` | `/api/seller-adjustments/:id` | â€” | Delete (requires `x-delete-password` header) |
